item.title: Fedora Project
item.description: "Fedora" is not only a kind of hat, but also a large Open Source community with a unique role in the Open Source ecosystem. This page provides an overview of the Fedora Linux distribution, project, and community. What is Fedora? Fedora is three different things, rolled into one. Linux kernel distribution Fedora is a Linux kernel distribution. The Linux kernel is just one part of a computer system.
